# --- Run snapshots (kept locally only; do not ship to the repo). ---
# Operator-report Markdown files in apps/api/_audit/ stay in git, but
# the per-run audit directories are too noisy + too large for the
# repo. Each run writes ~30 JSON files + a markdown report; the
# sample-report frontend page is fully self-contained so it doesn't
# need these on disk to render.
apps/api/_audit/live_runs/

# --- Frontend test artifacts ---
apps/web/coverage/
apps/web/playwright-report/
apps/web/test-results/
